divs: Sighting DetailsAs an amatuer astronomer,I was scanning the skies,and the object came intoview.Both lights I thought were sattillites.But the yell.-gold one moved backabout 1 degree and hovered.The second one bypassed the 1st one,on a N to Smovement,also.I got my camera out and started taking severalfotos,unfortuneately the film wasnt set for the dark.Then I just wentin,slightly shaken.Thats how I lost sight of it.
Summary: golden star-like ufo over San Francisco,this year
